[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "マリオン",
		"romanized_name": "Marion",
		"model_path_hash": "2676271994623593349",
		"text": "プラフタさん。設計の助けが必要かと思って、\nリリーを連れてきたわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5397390121100149522",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "リリー",
		"romanized_name": "Lilie",
		"model_path_hash": "3156259592327480116",
		"text": "どこまで力になれるか分かりませんが、\nあたしにも協力させてください！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1808607659247495452",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "助かります。ではまず、広い世界の中で「飴」の存在を\n検出する仕組みを検討したいのですが……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "リリー",
		"romanized_name": "Lilie",
		"model_path_hash": "3156259592327480116",
		"text": "「飴」は元々転移用の道具。転移するのに\n転移元の位置と、転移先の位置が必要となると……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1808607659247495452",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "リリー",
		"romanized_name": "Lilie",
		"model_path_hash": "3156259592327480116",
		"text": "「飴」自体に現在位置を検出する機能がありそうよね。\nそれを上手く利用すれば……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1808607659247495452",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "なるほど……その前提で検討してみましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ロジー",
		"romanized_name": "Logy",
		"model_path_hash": "3061836162665800468",
		"text": "二人とも、真剣だな。\n俺たちも機材製作担当として頑張らないと",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8747806484636614570",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "ええ。新式錬金術の使い手同士、力を合わせましょう",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "プラフタ",
		"romanized_name": "Plachta",
		"model_path_hash": "894414068988709786",
		"text": "お二人も、レシピを見て何か気付いたことがあったら\n教えてもらえると助かります",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8944192761651257696",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ミルカ",
		"romanized_name": "Miruca",
		"model_path_hash": "6658023269359396885",
		"text": "無駄な部分があればすぐに指摘するわ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1034358740077913276",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "ユーディットさん、ついにできたよ！　\nこれが「宝石パイプ追跡イタズラ装置」だ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "これでキースさんのパイプがある場所に、\n直接「何か」を送り込めるはずだよね？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "ふふふ、どんなイタズラを仕掛ける？　やっぱり、\nびっくり箱とか？　それとも……お菓子の山とか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "うーん、どうしようかな……あんまり怒らせると\n怖いし、でもちょっとは驚かせたいし……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "そういえば、リアスさんから猫の耳が生える薬が\nあるって聞いたような？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "猫の耳が生えたキースさん……見てみたいかも！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "よーし、決まり！\nリアスさんからもらって、送り付けてやろう！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]